The paper also mentions the use of deep learning methods for multi-label tasks, which suggests a connection to the computer vision (cs.CV) and natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses label space partitioning and division, which could be related to information retrieval (cs.IR).
